The singer married Cole in 2006, but they split three years later and their divorce was finalised in 2010.

She made her comments in an interview to promote her new album, A Million Lights, on Gaydar Radio.

As well as sharing her manifesto on marriage, she told listeners she believed her pet chihuahua, Buster, is gay. 

‘I think so … he likes male company – he’s just not interested in the females,’ she said.

